metadata.name: Big Сhanges
metadata.description:
"Big Сhanges" piese is inspired and based on my personal photo and one of the happiest and most difficult periods in my life. 

I want to introduce you to Katsumi and her cat Yuki and this is their first day in Yerevan Armenia.

I invite you to return to my memories. I hope I can share a piece of my happiness with you. 

Created by AIKN_OW  
October 19, 2021 
Based on my personal photo from Yerevan, Armenia.
2750x4891
